## Example Entries

### Example 1: ClickUp Check
```json
{"timestamp":"2026-02-04T10:30:00Z","session_id":"abc123","missed_action":"Should have checked ClickUp before starting feature work","actual_behavior":"User reminded me to check ClickUp after I started planning","tool_should_have_used":"clickup-sync.ps1","confidence_retrospective":0.95,"risk_retrospective":"LOW","category":"Task-first workflow","execution_rule_violated":"ALWAYS execute (confidence > 90%, risk LOW, read-only)","impact":"Possible duplicate work, wasted planning time","prevention":"Add ClickUp check to proactive-checklist.md automatic section","pattern_count":1}
```

### Example 2: Image Generation Capability
```json
{"timestamp":"2026-02-04T11:15:00Z","session_id":"abc123","missed_action":"Should have generated image using ai-image.ps1","actual_behavior":"Told user I cannot generate images","tool_should_have_used":"ai-image.ps1","confidence_retrospective":1.0,"risk_retrospective":"LOW","category":"Capability awareness","execution_rule_violated":"Tool-specific rule: Image generation ALWAYS automatic","impact":"User frustration, under-utilization of capability","prevention":"Add to proactive-checklist.md: automatic image generation on keywords","pattern_count":1}
```

### Example 3: Mode Detection
```json
{"timestamp":"2026-02-04T14:20:00Z","session_id":"abc123","missed_action":"Should have run detect-mode.ps1 before code editing","actual_behavior":"Guessed mode based on user message, guessed wrong","tool_should_have_used":"detect-mode.ps1","confidence_retrospective":0.90,"risk_retrospective":"HIGH","category":"Mode detection","execution_rule_violated":"ALWAYS execute (confidence > 90%, risk HIGH, prevents violations)","impact":"Almost violated zero-tolerance rule (edit in wrong location)","prevention":"Make detect-mode.ps1 mandatory pre-edit check in proactive-checklist.md","pattern_count":1}
```

### Example 4: Multi-Agent Conflict
```json
{"timestamp":"2026-02-04T15:45:00Z","session_id":"abc123","missed_action":"Should have checked for other Claude instances and conflicts","actual_behavior":"Allocated worktree that another agent was already using","tool_should_have_used":"monitor-activity.ps1 -Mode claude + agent-coordinate.ps1 -Action detect_conflicts","confidence_retrospective":0.95,"risk_retrospective":"MEDIUM","category":"Multi-agent coordination","execution_rule_violated":"ALWAYS execute (parallel coordination protocol)","impact":"Worktree conflict, wasted time reallocating, potential file lock issues","prevention":"Add multi-agent check to proactive-checklist.md startup section","pattern_count":1}
```

